* export getYourLocation function
* add 'Your location' option to inputA
rewrite render methods for select options
optimize options for date and time

* set default initialCenter when location request blocked
* deploy to GitHub Pages

* move state(option, time, date) to Sidebar component from App component
> * render map directory from Sidebar component instead of using state shouldUpdate
> * render map when Enter key hit on inputs
* create instance properties(google, directionsService) in Map component

* set initial Map center from current location
> * move state 'shouldUpdate' to App component from Map component
* set TravelMode from bestRoute
* get routes with date and time
